# -*- mode: conf-space; -*-
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# mail@tvoss.eu

IMAPStore default-remote
Host imap.migadu.com
User mail@tvoss.eu
PassCmd "vlt raw Email mail@tvoss.eu"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore default-local
Path ~/mail/mail@tvoss.eu/
Inbox ~/mail/mail@tvoss.eu/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel default
Far :default-remote:
Near :default-local:
Patterns *

