# thomasvoss@live.com

IMAPStore legacy-remote
Host outlook.office365.com
User thomasvoss@live.com
PassCmd "~/opt/mutt_oauth2/mutt_oauth2.py ~/var/cache/mutt-oauth2-outlook.token"
